description:
Files in this record: 
 Assembled transcriptome libraries (AU, Leaf; AV, Flower; AW, Root; Trinity, trimmed to 500bp). DGEN_RUB_AU_AV_AW_trinity_500bp.fasta 
 Data description. Daphne RNA-Seq data summary.pptx 
 &nbsp; 
 RNA from tissues (leaf, root, flower) of greenhouse grown Daphne genkwa was subject to RNA-seq (Illumina NextSeq500, paired-end 150 nt). 
 Total RNA was extracted from leaf, root and flower of mature D. genkwa plants using the Spectrum&trade; Plant Total RNA Kit (Sigma-Aldrich, St Louis, MO, USA). Residual DNA contamination was removed using the TURBO DNA-free&trade; kit (Thermo Fisher Scientific, Waltham, MA, USA). All sequencing was performed at the Research Technology Support Facility at Michigan State University.&nbsp; 
 The raw sequence reads for the Daphne genkwa transcriptomes (leaf, root, flower) are available from the National Center for Biotechnology Information Sequence Read Archive under BioProject PRJNA1024452 (accessions SRX21995907-09).&nbsp;

